                  @{bg shine}»»»»»»»» CONFIGURATION ««««««««««@{bg back}

   The MV Mail Door is consist of three parts need to be configured :

           @{" Mail Door " link "Mdoor" 0}

           @{"    SMB    " link "SMB" 0} (Select message bases)
           
